# AI Financial News Summarizer

An open-source AI project that summarizes financial news, earnings reports, and market updates using OpenAI models.

## Features

- Financial news summarization
- Earnings report analysis
- Market trend extraction
- AI-powered insights

## Tech Stack

- Python
- OpenAI API
- Requests

## Roadmap

### Phase 1
- Financial news summarization

### Phase 2
- Earnings report analysis

### Phase 3
- Portfolio monitoring

### Phase 4
- Web dashboard

